thereof ſhould come to any poſſeſſion above forbidden or] immediately upon ſuch abſence ſhall ceaſe and be void, and the Incumbent ſo offending ſhall, &c. loſe one years profit of his ſaid Benefice to be diſtributed by the Ordinary to the poor of the Pariſh.

